<p>Glipple, Inc., additionally, may provide different account type options for those users wishing for a deeper interaction with Glipple’s platform. Account holders and General Free Users may access the Glipple Platform by any of our several services:</p>

<p>Free Service (Non-Account): a free-of-charge service;</p>

<p>Artist Account: an account-based, free service provided for artists to upload to and distribute material over Glipple’s Platform;</p>

<p>Fan/Listener/General User Account: an account-based, free service provided for all non-artist members (fans/listeners/general users) to download, stream, and otherwise interact with the material on Glipple’s Platform;</p>

